         <div type="translation">
            <ab>a. <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">The memorial belongs to </supplied>
               <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Eu</supplied>arestos son of Acheos, in which my children <supplied reason="lost">will be buried, but
no-one</supplied> else <supplied reason="lost">is allowed</supplied>; anyone who dares <supplied reason="lost">to bury anyone in it, let
him give</supplied> to the most sacred treasury a pound of pure bullion.</ab>
            <ab>b. <supplied reason="lost">Here</supplied> lies <gap reason="lost" extent="4" unit="character"/>
